  "closed_at": null,
  "body": "请教各位，集成weex_sdk后，渲染容器的位置怎么设置？大小可以通过setSize。\r\n尝试自定义RenderContainer，设置 RelativeLayout.LayoutParams，代码如下：\r\n\r\n        RenderContainer container=new RenderContainer(this);\r\n        RelativeLayout.LayoutParams layoutParams=new RelativeLayout.LayoutParams(300,300);\r\n        layoutParams.addRule(RelativeLayout.BELOW,R.id.layoutHeader);\r\n        container.setLayoutParams(layoutParams);\r\n        container.setBackgroundColor(Color.BLUE);\r\n        mWXSDKInstance.setRenderContainer(container);\r\n\r\n目标是想放在某个控件的下面，如上设置无效。求解！",
  "closed_by": null
}
